In order to set the homepage with Webconverger, you need to pass a **boot option**. 

For example for setting the homepage [http://webconverger.com/](http://webconverger.com/).


1. Pop in the Webconverger CD
2. Boot machine... it should display quickly something like the image above
3. Press F1 to examine boot menu... (optional)
4. Type in `live homepage=http://webconverger.com/`
5. Press return to load Webconverger with the customized homepage 